name: First Pentacle of Jupiter [PentacleCoin]
description: Allow me to introduce the PentacleCoin! For all Magick, Mystery & Mythology Fans! All of the planetary Pentacles of Solomon - containing the power and the spirits of the seven ancient planets - redesigned & brought into the NFT World as the PentacleCoin! The first of the animated PentacleCoin Series is the first Pentacle of Jupiter. More will come soon. Every PentacleCoin is limited to 30 Coins.
